{"tid":578274,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有無人聽過くるり(Quruli) ?","createTime":"2018-03-02T13:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T16:53:14.000Z","uid":79120,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e411f136aab8ff05808ba977d0f5151e6d923660","tid":578274,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/210035_ced0bf6db1821e24cff1c9f18e2d6ff9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F210035_ced0bf6db1821e24cff1c9f18e2d6ff9.jpg&h=5bb49b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n團團轉樂團（日語：くるり；英語：Quruli）1996年於日本京都的立命館大學音樂性社團Rock Commune裡成立。創始團員有岸田繁（主唱、吉他）、佐藤征史（貝斯）與森信行（鼓）。1998年以單曲「東京」主流出道。成立以來，歷經團員更換，與優秀的樂手合作，不斷嘗試新的音樂表現，Quruli在現今搖滾樂壇裡依舊特立獨行，發揮其獨特的浮游感。而每張專輯的風格迥異，展現多樣化的音樂創作。Quruli音樂的醍醐味在於，旋律與歌詞貼近人的溫度。2011年6月，Quruli將音樂創作的重心移回家鄉京都。目前成員是岸田繁（主唱、吉他）、佐藤征史（貝斯）、Fan Fan（小喇叭）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%98%E5%9C%98%E8%BD%89%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%259C%2598&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d8947c9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%98%E5%9C%98%E8%BD%89%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%98</a>"},{"pid":"234329c8e44d9d6bc0c68f0ee12a37b20aa5c8a4","tid":578274,"uid":79120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"ばらの花<br />\n應該最多人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fpjIsylnvU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfpjIsylnvU8&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6f6721ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fpjIsylnvU8</a><br />\n<br />\nくるり代表曲 - 東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love